<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 21:12:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>紫金哥伦比亚金矿因自制炸弹袭击而停工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/zijin-halts-work-colombia-gold-mine-after-homemade-bomb-attack-2025-01-18/</link><description>紫金矿业周六表示，在武装分子携带自制炸弹破坏了一个关键电源后，该公司已暂停其位于哥伦比亚的布里蒂卡金矿的生产。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 20:36:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/zijin-halts-work-colombia-gold-mine-after-homemade-bomb-attack-2025-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>据 CNBC 报道，Perplexity AI 竞标与 TikTok US 合并</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/perplexity-ai-bids-merge-with-tiktok-us-cnbc-reports-2025-01-18/</link><description>据 CNBC 报道，Perplexity AI 周六要求 TikTok 的中国母公司字节跳动允许这家美国搜索引擎初创公司与 TikTok US 合并，并创建一个由两家公司和 New Capital Partners 合并的新实体。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 20:32:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/perplexity-ai-bids-merge-with-tiktok-us-cnbc-reports-2025-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普“很可能”给予 TikTok 90 天的禁令缓期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-will-most-likely-give-tiktok-90-day-reprieve-potential-ban-2025-01-18/</link><description>美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普周六表示，他“很可能”在周一上任后，给予 TikTok 90 天的缓期，使其免受美国可能实施的禁令的影响。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 17:41:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/trump-will-most-likely-give-tiktok-90-day-reprieve-potential-ban-2025-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾表示，东盟和中国必须开始解决南海规则的棘手问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-china-must-start-tackling-thorny-issues-south-china-sea-code-philippines-2025-01-18/</link><description>菲律宾高级外交官周六表示，东盟和中国应该通过解决棘手的“里程碑问题”，包括其范围以及是否具有法律约束力，在南海行为准则的制定上取得进展。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 12:32:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-china-must-start-tackling-thorny-issues-south-china-sea-code-philippines-2025-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普称周一可能会给 TikTok 90 天的缓刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-faces-us-ban-deadline-users-brace-fallout-2025-01-18/</link><description>该应用程序上的用户正在告别，一些人拍摄自己疯狂滚动或在可能的禁令之前与粉丝分享最后的秘密。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 11:08:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-faces-us-ban-deadline-users-brace-fallout-2025-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>毛里求斯总理询问查戈斯军事基地租赁协议的期限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/mauritius-pm-queries-duration-lease-deal-chagos-military-base-2025-01-18/</link><description>毛里求斯总理纳文·拉姆古兰对当地一家报纸表示，他对美英军事基地租约的期限提出了质疑，这是英国计划将查戈斯群岛的控制权割让给毛里求斯的谈判的一个有争议的因素。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 09:31:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/mauritius-pm-queries-duration-lease-deal-chagos-military-base-2025-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>台湾代表团向特朗普就职典礼致以“最崇高的祝福”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-delegation-take-highest-blessings-trump-inauguration-2025-01-18/</link><description>参加下周唐纳德·特朗普就任美国总统的台湾代表团团长周六表示，他将前往那里转达台湾对美国的“最高祝福”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 09:07:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/taiwan-delegation-take-highest-blessings-trump-inauguration-2025-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>VinFast 携高端电动 SUV 进军印度，与竞争对手抗衡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vinfast-enter-india-with-premium-electric-suv-take-rivals-2025-01-18/</link><description>越南电动汽车制造商 VinFast 将推出两款高端电动 SUV 进入印度市场，与本土竞争对手 Mahindra &amp;amp; Mahindra 以及已经在全球第三大汽车市场占有一席之地的中国比亚迪展开竞争。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 05:32:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vinfast-enter-india-with-premium-electric-suv-take-rivals-2025-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>习近平表示中越构建具有战略意义的命运共同体</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/xi-says-china-vietnam-build-community-with-shared-future-strategic-significance-2025-01-18/</link><description>据中国官方新华社周六报道，中国国家主席习近平表示，北京愿与河内共同打造具有战略意义的命运共同体。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jan 2025 03:59:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/xi-says-china-vietnam-build-community-with-shared-future-strategic-significance-2025-01-18/</guid></item><item><title>即将离任的 FCC 负责人表示，盐台风黑客攻击是解决安全问题的号角</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/outgoing-fcc-head-says-salt-typhoon-hacking-clarion-call-address-security-issues-2025-01-17/</link><description>即将离任的美国联邦通信委员会主席表示，与中国有关的针对美国电信公司的大规模网络间谍活动“盐台风”是解决重大电信安全问题的“号角”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 21:49:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/outgoing-fcc-head-says-salt-typhoon-hacking-clarion-call-address-security-issues-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>律师敦促白宫和司法部澄清应用商店可能会继续提供 TikTok</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/lawyer-urges-white-house-doj-clarify-app-stores-may-continue-offer-tiktok-2025-01-17/</link><description>TikTok 内容创作者的律师周五敦促白宫和司法部向苹果和谷歌澄清，周日法律禁令生效后，他们可以继续在应用商店提供 TikTok 短视频应用。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 21:08:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/lawyer-urges-white-house-doj-clarify-app-stores-may-continue-offer-tiktok-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>《原神》发行商与美国就侵犯儿童隐私指控达成和解</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/genshin-impact-maker-settles-us-charges-violating-childrens-privacy-2025-01-17/</link><description>动漫风格奇幻视频游戏“原神”的发行商 Cognosphere 已同意支付 2000 万美元，以和解美国联邦贸易委员会对该公司违反儿童隐私法的指控。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 20:16:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/genshin-impact-maker-settles-us-charges-violating-childrens-privacy-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 的奶油和糖果供应商受到美国禁令的威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktoks-purveyors-creams-candies-under-threat-us-ban-2025-01-17/</link><description>TikTok 表示，其美国网站为小型企业创造了数十亿美元的收入。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 19:26:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktoks-purveyors-creams-candies-under-threat-us-ban-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>拜登政府发布最后一刻规则限制低价值货运</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/biden-administration-posts-last-minute-rule-curb-low-value-shipments-2025-01-17/</link><description>拜登政府周五在最后一刻发布了拟议规则，将免税进口限制在 800 美元“最低限度”门槛以下，拒绝对受美国其他惩罚性关税征收的低价值货物豁免。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 18:23:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/biden-administration-posts-last-minute-rule-curb-low-value-shipments-2025-01-17/</guid></item><item><title>四国外长预计将在特朗普就职后第二天举行会议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/quad-foreign-ministers-expected-meet-day-after-trump-inauguration-2025-01-17/</link><description>知情人士称，美国国务卿以及澳大利亚、印度和日本外长预计将于周二在华盛顿举行会议，即当选总统唐纳德·特朗普就职后的第二天。</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 18:16:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/quad-foreign-ministers-expected-meet-day-after-trump-inauguration-2025-01-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>